<hw>Pug</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Hind. <ets>pag</ets>
foot.]</ety> <def>A footprint; a track; as of a boar.</def>
<mark>[India]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pug-faced</ent>⟦br⟧
